   <text type="card">
      <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1895_AS_RBH_1_00044.jpeg"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb338" type="place">I. Wollzeile 15</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1895_AS_RBH_1_00045.jpeg"/>Lieber Richard!</salute></opener><p>In der <rs ref="#pmb42262" type="org"><hi rend="latintype">Meier</hi>iſchen Strohhuthandlung</rs> am <rs ref="#pmb8" type="place">Prater</rs>, glaub ich oder <rs ref="#pmb42024" type="place">Freiſingergaſſe</rs>. –</p><p>Ob ich hingehe, weiſs ich nicht. Hab’ auch keine Einladung. Heut bin ich jedenfalls im <rs ref="#pmb34" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Griensteidl</hi></rs>.</p><closer>Herzlichſt Ihr<signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body>
